o%20ship%20headed%20from%20Turkey%20to%20India%20via%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20that%20took%20place%20on%20Sunday%20(November%2019)%2C%20has%20raised%20fears%20of%20escalated%20regional%20tensions%20over%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20Houthis%2C%20an%20Iran-backed%20rebel%20movement%20in%20Yemen%20that%20threatened%20earlier%20Sunday%20to%20target%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fworld%2Findia-bound-cargo-ship-seized-houthis-in-red-sea-israel-9033813%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20Houthi%20rebels%20are%20also%20suspected%20of%20having%20sent%20missiles%20and%20drones%20over%20the%20shipping%20lane%20of%20the%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20while%20calling%20the%20incident%20an%20%E2%80%9CIranian%20act%20of%20terror%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20that%20there%20were%20no%20Israelis%20onboard%20the%20ship%20that%20has%2025%20crew%20members%20of%20various%20nationalities%2C%20including%20Bulgarians%2C%20Filipinos%2C%20Mexicans%20and%20Ukrainians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20called%20the%20hijacking%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20grave%20incident%20of%20global%20consequence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hijacked%20vessel%20had%20been%20in%20Korfez%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20Pipavav%2C%20India%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20seizure%20reported%20by%20Israel%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fworld%2Findia-bound-cargo-ship-seized-houthis-in-red-sea-israel-9033813%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Israel%20has%20denied%20any%20connection%20with%20the%20seized%20ship%2C%20unconfirmed%20reports%20suggest%20the%20ship%20may%20have%20an%20Israeli%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20officials%20insisted%20the%20ship%20was%20British-owned%20and%20Japanese-operated.%20However%2C%20ownership%20details%20in%20public%20shipping%20databases%20associated%20the%20ship%E2%80%99s%20owners%20with%20Ray%20Car%20Carriers%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Abraham%20%E2%80%9CRami%E2%80%9D%20Ungar%2C%20who%20is%20known%20as%20one%20of%20the%20richest%20men%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUngar%20denied%20comment%20to%20the%20Associated%20Press%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20British%20military%E2%80%99s%20United%20Kingdom%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%2C%20which%20provides%20warnings%20to%20sailors%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%20and%20the%20wider%20region%2C%20the%20hijacking%20occurred%20nearly%20150%20kilometers%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20port%20city%20of%20Hodeida%2C%20near%20the%20coast%20of%20Eritrea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20have%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20target%20Israeli%20ships%20in%20the%20waters%20off%20Yemen%20in%20wake%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20relentless%20bombing%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700464724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F17123254%2Fcontainer-ship-560789_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bound-cargo-ship-in-red-sea%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20Houthis%2C%20an%20Iran-backed%20rebel%20movement%20in%20Yemen%20that%20had%20earlier%20threatened%20to%20target%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-alleges-houthi-rebel-hand-behind-hijacking-of-india-bo