ife-balance-indian-it-sector-employees-forced-to-work-50-hours-a-week%2Farticleshow%2F105348271.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ONGC%20To%20Start%20Crude%20Oil%20Production%20In%20KG%20Basin%20Next%20Week%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20state-owned%20Oil%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20Corporation%20(ONGC)%20will%20start%20the%20production%20of%20crude%20oil%20from%20its%20flagship%20deep-water%20project%20in%20Krishna%20Godavari%20Basin%20next%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20production%20will%20help%20India%20save%20nearly%20Rs%2011%2C000%20crore%20per%20year.%20India%20imports%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20crude%20oil%20requirements%20and%20about%20half%20of%20its%20natural%20gas%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EONGC%20also%20plans%20a%20capital%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20crore%20for%20petrochemical%20projects%20by%202028-2030.%20The%20investment%20will%20be%20used%20for%20two%20separate%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20in%20KG%20Basin%20is%20considered%20very%20significant%2C%20say%20top%20officials%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Petroleum%20and%20Natural%20Gas%20(MPNG).%20The%20production%20from%20its%20much-publicised%20deep%20sea%20asset%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20explorer%20and%20help%20reverse%20the%20low%20productions%20bothering%20the%20state-owned%20hydrocarbon%20behemoth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstrologers%20say%20the%20time%20between%20November%2020%20and%20November%2026%20is%20a%20very%20special%20moment%20for%20projects%20in%20India%2C%20there%20are%20chances%20of%20new%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20domestic%20output%20will%20also%20help%20save%20outflow%20of%20precious%20foreign%20exchange%20on%20import%20of%20crude%20oil.%20At%20current%20Brent%20crude%20price%20of%20%2477.4%2C%20this%20output%20alone%20will%20save%20Rs%2029%20crore%20every%20day%20(at%20Rs%2083.29%20to%20%241)%20or%20a%20staggering%20Rs10%2C600%20crore%20on%20an%20annual%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20oil%20production%20from%20the%20basin%20was%20scheduled%20to%20start%20from%20November%202021%2C%20but%20the%20deadline%20was%20delayed%20several%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20this%20will%20be%20ONGC's%20first%20significant%20oil%20producing%20asset%20on%20the%20East%20Coast.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KG-DWN-98%2F2%20block%20has%20a%20number%20of%20discoveries%20that%20have%20been%20clubbed%20into%20clusters.%20It%20is%20situated%2035%20km%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20with%20water%20depths%20up%20to%203%2C200%20metres.%20The%20discoveries%20in%20the%20block%20are%20divided%20into%20three%20clusters%20-%20Cluster-1%2C%202%20and%203.%20Cluster%202%20is%20being%20put%20to%20production%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20crude%20oil%20output%2C%207-8%20mmscmd%20(million%20metric%20standard%20cubic%20metres%20per%20day)%20of%20gas%20will%20start%20to%20flow%20from%20the%20middle%20of%20calendar%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hydrocarbon%20giant%2C%20it%20is%20reliably%20learnt%2C%20will%20press%20into%20service%20as%20many%20as%2075%20rigs.%20ONGC%20plans%20to%20start%20producing%20from%20three%20to%20four%20wells%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%2C%20when%20the%20production%20could%20be%208%2C000%20to%209%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day.%20The%20company%20actually%20aims%20to%20drill%20541%20oil%20wells%20in%20FY24%2C%20up%20from%20461%20wells%20drilled%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20production%20from%20the%20KG-DWN-98%2F2%20block%20will%20add%20to%20India's%20domestic%20production%20and%20help%20reduce%20the%20dependence%20on%20imports%20to%20some%20extent.%20India%20currently%20produces%20approximately%20600%2C000%20barrels%20of%20oil%20per%20day.%20Thus%2C%20at%20peak%2C%20the%20cluster-2%20project%20will%20account%20for%207%25%20of%20India's%20output.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20start.%20Peak%20oil%20production%20of%2045%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day%20is%20expected%20sometime%20in%20FY%2024-25.%20At%20the%20peak%20output%20of%2045%2C000%20barrels%20per%20day%2C%20this%20will%20be%20the%20third%20most%20prolific%20offshore%20asset%20for%20ONGC%20after%20Mumbai%20High%20and%20Bassein%20%26amp%3B%20Satellite%20fields%2C%20both%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20top%20ministry%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20combination%20of%20fresh%20output%20and%20enhanced%20recoveries%2C%20ONGC%20group's%20oil%20production%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%20to%20top%2025%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY25%20compared%20to%2021.5%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EONGC%20has%20seen%20a%20fall%20in%20its%20crude%20oil%20output%20as%20most%20of%20the%20assets%20are%20mature%20and%20a%20natural%20decline%20has%20set%20in.%20Even%20as%20ONGC%20is%20investing%20in%20technology%20for%20enhanced%20oil%20recovery%20and%20improved%20oil%20recovery%2C%20the%20commencement%20of%20output%20from%20new%20assets%20like%20the%20KG%20block%20will%20certainly%20reverse%20the%20trend%20of%20falling%20output.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Q2%2C%20ONGC's%20consolidated%20net%20profit%20soared%20142.4%20percent%20at%20Rs%2016%2C553%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20ONGC%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20bring%20in%20an%20equity%20partner%20in%20ONGC%20Petro%20additions%20Limited%20(OPaL)%20by%20financial%20year%202026-2027.%20ONGC%20had%20then%20said%20it%20wants%20to%20infuse%20Rs%2018%2C365%20crore%20in%20OPaL%2C%20and%20make%20OPaL%20a%20joint%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOPaL%20is%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20ONGC%2C%20GAIL%20(India)%20and%20Gujarat%20State%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Limited%20(GSPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700463060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fiju3i0l8_oil-generic_625x300_17_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A