n%20the%20line%20to%20stop%20the%20ball%20from%20running%20towards%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20hailed%20Kohli%20for%20his%20on-field%20magic%20and%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20BCCI%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20tournament%20I%20think%20we%20took%20some%20brilliant%20catches%20but%20what%20I%20really%20liked%20is%20the%20brotherhood%20we%20shared%20on%20the%20field.%20The%20way%20each%20one%20supported%20each%20other%20the%20way%20everyone%20was%20backing%20that's%20outstanding%20to%20see%20and%20I%20see%20only%20growing%20up%20as%20a%20team%20on%20the%20field%20and%20today's%20winner%20he's%20been%20a%20terrific%20player.%20He%20sets%20himself%20up%20great%20standards%20and%20every%20time%20he%20goes%20on%20the%20field%20he%20does%20magic%20and%20the%20best%20part%20is%20that%20he%20not%20only%20does%20his%20job%20so%20well%20but%20his%20actions%20inspire%20so%20many%20people%20and%20it%20is%20none%20other%20than%20Virat%20Kohli.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDilip%20also%20made%20an%20inspirational%20speech%20to%20cheer%20up%20the%20players%20ensuring%20that%20even%20after%20ending%20up%20on%20the%20losing%20side%20the%20players%20can%20be%20proud%20of%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20I%20know%20it%20is%20tough%20and%20we%20all%20feel%20the%20pain%20but%20that's%20what%20it%20is.%20We%20did%20everything%20possibly%20right%20and%20still%20the%20result%20is%20not%20in%20our%20favour.%20But%20I%20think%20Rahul%20(Dravid)%20bhai%20said%20we%20can%20all%20be%20proud%20of%20ourselves.%20I%20appreciate%20and%20thank%20every%20player%20in%20this%20group%20who%20have%20committed%20in%20the%20practice%20sessions.%20The%20way%20you%20put%20yourself%20on%20the%20line%2C%20you%20put%20intent%20and%20energy.%20I%20couldn't%20ask%20more%20than%20this.%20Well%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Dilip%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20dat