estigation%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhindenburg-shorts-adani-group-flags-debt-and-accounting-concerns%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20accounting%20fraud%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20within%20the%20specified%20timeframe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fplea-in-supreme-court-for-contempt-action-against-sebi-for-not-completing-probe-in-adani-hindenburg-matter-242513%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%3Cem%3E%20LiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20advocate%20Vishal%20Tiwari%2C%20one%20of%20the%20individuals%20who%20filed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20seeking%20a%20court-monitored%20inquiry%20into%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20the%20conglomerate%20by%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research.%20Tiwari%20highlighted%20that%20according%20to%20the%20May%2017%20order%20of%20the%20top%20court%2C%20SEBI%20was%20required%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20August%2014.%20However%2C%20the%20market%20regulator%20has%20not%20yet%20presented%20its%20final%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20sought%20a%20directive%20asking%20SEBI%20to%20explain%20its%20non-compliance%20and%20also%20the%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20regulator.%20He%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20which%20also%20accused%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20of%20irregularities.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-allegations-sc-appointed-panel-submits-report-in-a-sealed-cover%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court-appointed%20expert%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20also%20investigate%20the%20OCCRP%20report%2C%20Tiwari%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20LiveLaw%2C%20while%20the%20scheduled%20hearing%20into%20the%20matter%20was%20on%20August%2029%2C%202023%2C%20the%20case%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20listed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Senior%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20had%20raised%20the%20matter%20before%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20November%206%2C%20expressing%20urgency.%20The%20CJI%20assured%20that%20the%20issue%20would%20be%20examined%20with%20the%20registry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20two-month%20deadline%20set%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20investigate%20the%20allegations%20raised%20by%20Hindenburg%20ended%20on%20May%202.%20SEBI%20requested%20an%20extension%2C%20citing%20the%20complexity%20of%20transactions%20and%20the%20need%20for%20additional%20time%2C%20and%20was%20granted%20time%20until%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700461043000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F11165427%2FSupreme_Court_of_India_inside_bulidings_01.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-plea-supreme-court-contempt-sebi-delay-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20application%20highlighted%20that%20according%20to%20the%20May%2017%20order%20of%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20market%20regulator%20was%20required%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20by%20August%2014.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadani-hindenburg-plea-supreme-court-contempt-sebi-delay-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20woman%20teacher%20booked%20for%20'converting'%20Class%20X%20boy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700460944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105347914%2Cimgsize-42082.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkanpur%2Fwoman-teacher-booked-in-kanpur-for-converting-sexually-exploiting-class-x-boy%2Farticleshow%2F105347614.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkanpur%2Fwoman-teacher-booked-in-kanpur-for-converting-sexually-exploiting-class-x-boy%2Farticleshow%2F105347614.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Bayer%20Is%20Delivering%20Medical%20Care%20at%20the%20Doorsteps%20of%20Rural%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Bayer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20rural%20healthcare%20system%20is%20strained%20due%20to%20a%20severe%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20and%20infrastructure.%20The%20Government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhmis.mohfw.gov.in%2Fdownloadfile%3Ffilepath%3Dpublications%2FRural-Health-Statistics%2FRHS%25202021-22.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERural%20Health%20Statistics%202021-2022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20a%20deficit%20of%2079.5%20percent%20in%20rural%20healthcare%20specialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrimary%20Health%20Centres%20(PHC)%2C%20the%20initial%20point%20of%20care%20for%20villages%2C%20cater%20to%20around%2036%2C000%20people%20per%20PHC%2C%20as%20per%20the%20same%20report.%20PHCs%20typically%20have%20one%20medical%20officer%20who%20is%20a%20physician%2C%20staff%20nurses%2C%20and%20Auxiliary%20Nurses%20and%20Midwives%20(ANM)%20along%20with%20other%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInadequate%20infrastructure%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316087%2Fassam-couple-helps-rural-northeast-india-access-affordable-mental-healthcare-mita%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20patient%20load%3C%2Fa%3E%20contribute%20to%20significant%20stress%20on%20doctors%20and%20nurses.%20Villagers%20have%20to%20travel%20for%20about%2045%20minutes%20to%20reach%20the%20nearest%20district%20hospital%20to%20access%20a%20specialist.%20To%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20established%20telemedicine%20centres%20at%20PHCs%20to%20bring%20top%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20local%20communities%2C%20right%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20Bahl%20%E2%80%94%20Country%20Group%20CSR%20Head%2C%20Bayer%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20Director%2C%20Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20many%20districts%20across%20the%20country%20like%20Raichur%2C%20Khandwa%2C%20and%20Tikamgarh%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20there%20was%20very%20little%20support%20available%20in%20PHCs.%20People%20have%20to%20travel%20several%20kilometres%20just%20to%20see%20a%20specialist%2C%20and%20many%20may%20not%20go.%20So%20we%20realised%20that%20rather%20than%20building%20something%20new%2C%20we%20should%20make%20healthcare%20better%2C%20affordable%20and%20accessible%20right%20at%20the%20PHC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Bayer%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%2014%20aspirational%20districts%20(a%20programme%20by%20the%20government%20to%20improve%20underdeveloped%20districts%20nationwide)%20across%20eight%20states%2C%20Sarita%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20health%20index%20of%20the%20rural%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer's%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer2-2-1700285677-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20consultation%20with%20specialists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20telemedicine%20centres%20set%20up%20within%20the%20PHCs%2C%20offer%20around%2020%20distinct%20medical%20specialities%20via%20teleconsultation.%20The%20centres%20include%20a%20trained%20GNM%20(General%20Nursing%20and%20Midwifery)%20and%20a%20centre%20coordinator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Sarita%20explains%2C%20when%20a%20patient%20requires%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316871%2Ffriends-launch-digiqure-teleconsultation-startup-affordable-rural-healthcare-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especialist%E2%80%99s%20opinion%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20are%20directed%20to%20the%20telemedicine%20centre%2C%20often%20located%20in%20the%20adjacent%20room%20within%20the%20PHC.%20Here%2C%20the%20nurse%20links%20the%20patients%20to%20the%20specialist%20via%20a%20video%20call%20after%20examining%20their%20vital%20signs%20and%20medical%20background.%20Post%20the%20consultation%2C%20the%20nurse%20issues%20a%20printed%20prescription%20to%20the%20patient%2C%20who%20can%20purchase%20the%20prescribed%20medications%20from%20the%20PHC%20pharmacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer3-1700285786-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20telemedicine%20centres%20offer%20easy%20access%20to%20doctors%20to%20villagers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalguni%2C%20the%20ANM%20at%20the%20Phygital%20in%20Chhiri%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20emphasises%20the%20significant%20benefits%20that%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20has%20brought%20to%20the%20local%20community%20and%20nearby%20villages.%20She%20highlights%20that%20patients%20from%20remote%20villages%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20endure%20the%20trouble%20of%20travelling%20and%20spending%20an%20entire%20day%20at%20the%20district%20hospital.%20With%20the%20convenience%20of%20accessing%20various%20specialists%20through%20telemedicine%20centres%2C%20patients%20have%20readily%20embraced%20this%20solution.%20She%20notes%20that%20their%20PHC%20witnesses%20over%2090%20teleconsultation%20cases%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hanifa%20Batterywala%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20doctor%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTelemedicine%20helps%20us%20reach%20even%20remote%20areas%20where%20often%20patients%20are%20daily%20wage%20workers%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20lose%20an%20entire%20day%20to%20travel%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20suffering%20from%20chronic%20itching%20for%20two%20months%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20ANM%2C%20Falguni%2C%20and%20she%20booked%20a%20video%20consultation%20with%20a%20dermatologist.%20The%20doctor%20prescribed%20a%20lotion%20and%20a%20medicine.%20My%20itching%20reduced%20in%20just%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20and%20I%20have%20faced%20no%20problem%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sonal%20Patel%2C%20a%20patient%20from%20Chirri.%20Falguni%20adds%20that%20most%20patients%20seek%20help%20for%20skin%20allergies%20or%20paediatric%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20limited%20timings%20of%20the%20PHCs%2C%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20centres%20operate%20from%20nine%20to%20five%2C%20providing%20access%20to%20physicians%2C%20gynaecologists%2C%20cardiologists%2C%20ENT%20specialists%2C%20dermatologists%2C%20paediatricians%2C%20and%20other%20experts%20via%20teleconsultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDiagnosing%20silent%20killers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20conducts%20several%20awareness%20camps%20in%20rural%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FBayer1-1700285903-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334466%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBayer%20conducts%20monthly%20health%20camps%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20non-communicable%20diseases.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayer%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20of%20data%20collected%20from%20all%20the%20PHCs%20suggested%20that%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20cases%20at%20the%20centres%20constituted%20non-communicable%20diseases%20(NCDs)%20such%20as%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20prevalence%20of%20diabetes%20and%20hypertension%20is%20rapidly%20increasing%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1944600%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20ICMR-INDIAB%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20estimates%20the%20numbers%20to%20be%20101%20million%20and%20136%20million%2C%20respectively.%20The%20study%20also%20highlights%20that%20more%20than%20one-third%20of%20Indians%20are%20affected%20by%20hypertension%2C%20with%20a%20high%20prevalence%20of%20prediabetes%20observed%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiabetes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20associated%20NCDs%20can%20lead%20to%20cardiovascular%20complications%20and%20other%20health%20issues%20such%20as%20kidney%2C%20foot%2C%20and%20eye%20diseases.%20The%20report%20emphasises%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20early%20diagnosis%2C%20prevention%20and%20treatment%20to%20reduce%20fatalities%20caused%20by%20these%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20on%20these%20tenets%20is%20a%20major%20part%20of%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20today.%20They%20organise%20monthly%20health%20camps%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20diabetes%2C%20hypertension%2C%20various%20heart%20conditions%2C%20breast%20cancer%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarita%20informs%20that%20since%20April%202022%2C%20they%20have%20organised%20over%20539%20health%20camps%2C%20reached%206%2C000%20villages%2C%20and%20assisted%20over%201%2C70%2C000%20beneficiaries%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20These%20camps%20involved%20over%2095%2C000%20general%20consultations%20and%2074%2C000%20specialist%20consultations.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20no%20disease%20goes%20undiagnosed%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20resources%20or%20awareness.%20Quality%20health%20care%20should%20be%20available%20to%20every%20person%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sarita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700460854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayer%20Foundation%20India%20(BFI)%20has%20set%20up%2028%20%E2%80%98Phygital%E2%80%99%20telemedicine%20centres%20in%20villages%20of%208%20states%20to%20provide%20easy%20access%20to%20quality%20medical%20care.%20It%20is%20also%20conducting%20health%20camps%20for%20early%20diagnosis%20of%20breast%20cancer%2C%20hypertension%20and%20diabetes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Ackman%20is%20defending%20Elon%20Musk%20amid%20the%20X%20owner's%20antisemitism%20controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigur