l-devices-123112000195_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Silence%20Of%20Crowd%20When%20Virat%20Kohli%20Got%20Out%20Was%20Most%20Satisfying%3A%20Pat%20Cummins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20deafening%20silence%20of%20over%2090%2C000%20supporters%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%2C%20as%20Pat%20Cummins%20snuffed%20out%20the%20peerless%20Virat%20Kohli%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20was%20perhaps%20the%20%26quot%3Bsweetest%20moment%26quot%3B%20the%20Australian%20skipper%20has%20ever%20experienced%20on%20a%20cricket%20field.%20After%20becoming%20the%20fifth%20Australian%20captain%20to%20secure%20his%20country's%20sixth%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Cummins%20admitted%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bfallen%20in%20love%20with%2050-over%20format%20all%20over%20again%26quot%3B.%20He%20got%20Kohli%2C%20who%20was%20well-set%20on%2054%2C%20with%20a%20delivery%20that%20had%20an%20extra%20bounce%20and%20the%20premier%20India%20batter%20played%20on%20trying%20to%20jab%20it%20towards%20the%20covers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYeah%2C%20I%20think%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20nodded%20in%20affirmative%20when%20asked%20if%20the%20silence%20was%20his%20sweetest%20experience%20on%20a%20cricket%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20going%20against%20their%20custom%2C%20the%20Aussies%20had%20a%20second%20huddle%20to%20just%20acknowledge%20how%20big%20the%20moment%20in%20the%20game%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20take%20a%20second%20in%20the%20huddle%20just%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20silence%20that%20was%20going%20around%20the%20crowd.%20It%20just%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20days%20where%20it%20was%20all%20made%20for%20him%20to%20score%20another%20hundred%20like%20he%20normally%20does%20and%20that%20was%20satisfying%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20that%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20as%20it%20hs%20got%20its%20own%20legacy%20and%20also%20players%20have%20their%20stories%20to%20tell%20and%20perhaps%2C%20it%20is%20the%20bilateral%20series%20that%20become%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20must%20say%2C%20maybe%20because%20we%20won%2C%20I%20did%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20ODI%20again%20this%20World%20Cup.%20I%20think%20the%20scenario%20where%20every%20game%20really%20matters%2C%20it%20does%20mean%20a%20bit%20different%20to%20just%20a%20bilateral%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20acknowledged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20mean%2C%20the%20World%20Cup's%20got%20such%20rich%20history%2C%20I'm%20sure%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20around%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Yeah%2C%20there's%20so%20many%20wonderful%20games%2C%20so%20many%20wonderful%20stories%20within%20this%20last%20couple%20of%20months.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20definitely%20a%20place.%E2%80%9D%20He%20lost%20his%20mother%20in%20March%2C%20during%20a%20tour%20of%20India%2C%20which%20he%20had%20to%20curtail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20returned%2C%20leading%20the%20country%20to%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20title%2C%20secured%20the%20coveted%20Ashes%2C%20and%20now%20clinched%20what%20he%20termed%20the%20%26quot%3Bpinnacle%20of%20this%20sport%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20'Captain%20Marvel'%20has%20accomplished%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYeah%2C%20I%20mean%20at%20this%20moment%20just%20incredibly%20proud%20really%20of%20the%20year%20we've%20had.%20I%20have%20obviously%20had%20a%20really%20big%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20about%20the%20sacrifices%20made%20by%20everyone%20in%20the%20team%20and%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20know%20my%20family%20at%20home%20is%20watching%2C%20just%20got%20a%20message%20from%20dad%20saying%20he's%20had%20a%20lot%20of%204am%20wake%20ups%2C%20not%20going%20to%20bed%20until%204am%2C%20so%20he's%20as%20pumped%20as%20anything.%20So%20yeah%2C%20you%20sacrifice%20a%20lot%20to%20play%20for%20Australia.%E2%80%9D%20But%20this%20was%20also%20about%20going%20through%20all%20of%20that%20in%20search%20of%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20in%20the%20team%20has%20and%20we've%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20year%20away%20but%20we%20do%20it%20for%20these%20moments%20and%20my%20wife%20and%20two%20girls%20are%20probably%20asleep%2C%20but%20they're%20all%20pumped%2C%20they%20do%20the%20journey%20with%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20everyone's%20got%20their%20own%20story%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20proud%20people%20out%20there%20in%20our%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cummins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20his%20hotel%20room%2C%20he%20saw%20Indian%20supporters%2C%20all%20clad%20in%20blue%2C%20walk%20towards%20the%20stadium.%20He%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20nervous%20energy%2C%20pacing%20up%20and%20down%20in%20his%20hotel%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20like%20to%20say%20I'm%20pretty%20relaxed%20but%20I%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20nervous%20this%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admitted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20pacing%20around%2C%20waiting%20for%20it%20to%20start%2C%20seeing%20the%20sea%20of%20blue%20in%20the%20hotel%20getting%20closer%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObserving%20the%20sea%20of%20blue%2C%20cars%20parked%20with%20selfie%20cameras%20out%2C%20you%20knew%20you%20were%20walking%20into%20something%20pretty%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20Cummins%20described%20his%20experience%20before%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20to%20walk%20out%20for%20the%20toss%20and%20just%20see%20130%2C000%20blue%20Indian%20shirts%2C%20it's%20an%20experience%20you'll%20never%20forget.%20Awesome%20day%20and%20the%20good%20thing%20was%20they%20weren't%20too%20noisy%20for%20most%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20attendance%20for%20the%20match%20was%2092%2C543.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHead%20gamble%20pays%20off%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20all%20the%20emot