mistic%26quot%3B%20it%20could%20bring%20back%20Altman%20and%20other%20key%20employees%20who%20left%2C%20Chief%20Strategy%20Officer%20Jason%20Kwon%20said%20in%20a%20memo%20to%20staff%2C%20the%20Information%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGreg%20Brockman%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrockman%2C%20who%20co-founded%20OpenAI%20eight%20years%20ago%20in%20his%20apartment%2C%20quit%20as%20president%20on%20Friday%20hours%20after%20the%20board%20pushed%20out%20Altman.%20Brockman%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20the%20social%20media%20site%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20today's%20news%2C%20I%20quit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrockman%20had%20been%20due%20to%20step%20down%20from%20his%20role%20as%20board%20chairman%20but%20stay%20on%20at%20the%20company%2C%20reporting%20to%20the%20new%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMira%20Murati%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20appointed%20Murati%20as%20interim%20CEO%20after%20the%20company%20ousted%20Altman.%20She%20wrote%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bhonored%20and%20humbled%26quot%3B%20to%20take%20up%20the%20position%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20important%20for%20OpenAI%20to%20remain%20%26quot%3Bfocused%2C%20driven%2C%20and%20true%20to%20our%20core%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20seen%20by%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20the%20Albanian-born%2C%20Dartmouth-educated%20engineer%20helped%20develop%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20best-known%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatya%20Nadella%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Microsoft%20CEO%20reached%20out%20to%20Altman%20following%20the%20firing%20to%20offer%20him%20support%20in%20his%20next%20steps%2C%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20situation%20told%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20is%20OpenAI's%20largest%20investor%20with%20a%20stake%20worth%20more%20than%20%2410%20billion.%20Nadella%20succeeded%20Steve%20Ballmer%20as%20Microsoft%20CEO%20in%202014.%3