ts'%20apartment%20in%20the%20town%20was%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20a%20building%2C%20above%20a%20local%20bar%20called%20the%20Stag%2C%20local%20historian%20Florian%20Kotanko%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F748588026%2Fa-long-legal-battle-over-hitlers-birth-home-in-austria-ends%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20NPR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hitler%20was%20in%20power%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20apartment%20was%20used%20as%20an%20art%20gallery%20and%20library%2C%20per%20NPR.%20During%20the%20same%20time%20period%2C%20it%20became%20a%20pilgrimage%20spot%20for%20his%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20boarded%20up%20for%20years%20after%20the%20war%2C%20it%20was%20a%20bank%20and%20a%20school.%20Finally%2C%20before%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ots.at%2Fpresseaussendung%2FOTS_20190805_OTS0056%2Fbmi-hitler-haus-prozess-zur-entschaedigung-fuer-die-enteignung-gewonnen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchase%20by%20the%20Austrian%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20it%20was%20a%20center%20for%20people%20with%20special%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20October%2C%20the%20government%20began%20developing%20the%20building%20into%20a%20police%20station%20set%20to%20open%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20the%20plans%20firmly%20in%20motion%2C%20a%20poll%20showed%2053%25%20of%20Austrians%20wished%20the%20site%20would%20be%20turned%20into%20an%20educational%20and%20historical%20site%20that%20addressed%20the%20history%20of%20National%20Socialism%2C%20especially%20in%20Austria%2C%20and%20anti-fascist%20measures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fmay%2F24%2Faustria-to-use-hitler-birthplace-braunau-am-inn-for-police-human-rights-training%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20Guardian.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2020%25%20of%20residents%20worry%20that%20while%20the%20building%20stands%2C%20it%20could%20serve%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20shrine%20for%20neo-Nazis%20or%20far-right%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20wish%20it%20would%20be%20torn%20out%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20government%20commission%20worried%20that%20tearing%20it%20down%20would%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20denial%20of%20Austria's%20involvement%20with%20Nazis%2C%20per%20the%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Austrian%20Commission%20on%20the%20Historically%20Correct%20Treatment%20of%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20Birthplace%20said%20in%20its%20final%20report%20that%20the%20building%20should%20not%20be%20associated%20with%20Hitler%20to%20deprive%20it%20of%20%26quot%3Bits%20symbolic%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F19%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Faustria-germany-hitler-birthplace.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResident%20Annette%20Pommer%20called%20the%20building%20of%20a%20police%20station%20a%20%26quot%3Bmissed%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20about%20how%20people%20become%20Hitler.%20It's%20not%20a%20house%20of%20evil.%20It's%20just%20a%20house%20where%20a%20child%20was%20born.%20But%20it's%20right%20to%20explain%20what%20became%20of%20that%20child.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20Austrian%20filmmaker%20G%C3%BCnter%20Schwaiger%2C%20agreed%2C%20saying%20the%20site%20could%20show%20how%20Nazis%20came%20from%20ordinary%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20close%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20house%20and%20to%20change%20the%20facade%20means%20only%20to%20continue%20the%20politics%20of%20repression%20of%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BThis%20house%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20symbol%20for%20a%20normal%20place%20in%20a%20normal%20little%20city%20%E2%80%94%20stands%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20Nazis%20didn't%20come%20from%20outside%20or%20from%20'another%20planet.'%20They%20came%20from%20our%20midst.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20say%20it's%20important%20for%20Austrians%20to%20accept%20the%20country's%20role%20in%20Hitler's%20abuses%2C%20despite%20some%20resistance%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20never%20forget%20the%20beginning%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20be%20aware%20of%20when%20things%20are%20getting%20problematic%2C%20and%20they%20are%20nowadays%2C%26quot%3B%20Eveline%20Doll%2C%20a%20native%20of%20the%20town%2C%20told%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustrians-hitler-braunau-apartment-neo-nazi-world-war-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700453820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655acbe79c7d23cb3b9d2cd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustrians-hitler-braunau-apartment-neo-nazi-world-war-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20some%20want%20it%20turned%20into%20an%20educational%20memorial%2C%20officials%20in%20Braunau%2C%20Austria%2C%20are%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20police%20station%20in%20its%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22scahill%40businessinsider.com%20(Sebastian%20Cahill)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustrians-hitler-braunau-apartment-neo-nazi-world-war-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Morgan%20Wallen%2C%20Taylor%20Swift%20Win%20Big%20at%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700452800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMixCollage-19-Nov-2023-03-15-PM-1017.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235801309%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Morgan%20Wallen%20and%20Taylor%20Swift%20were%20the%20big%20winners%20at%20the%202023%20Billboard%20Music%20Awards%2C%20which%20