2%80%99%20team%20was%20deemed%20destined%20to%20win%20just%20because%20we%20have%20%E2%80%98waited%E2%80%99%20too%20long.%20As%20part%20of%20our%20much%20proclaimed%20national%20%E2%80%98march%E2%80%99%20to%20glory%20and%20power%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20have%20concluded%20that%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20owed%20us%20a%20World%20Cup%20trophy.%20As%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPunjab%20Kesari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(that%20authentic%20voice%20of%20the%20Hindi%20heartland)%20headline%20put%20it%20on%20Sunday%20morning%3A%20%E2%80%98It%20was%20time%20to%20get%20even%20%5B%20with%20Australia%5D.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20every%20reason%20to%20feel%20proud%20of%20their%20campaign%2C%20winning%20the%20first%20nine%20matches%20of%20the%20tournament.%20But%20since%20the%20Cup%20has%20eluded%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20he%20and%20his%20colleagues%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20be%20skewered%20by%20the%20Monday-morning%20quarterbacks.%20In%20our%20collective%20boorishness%2C%20we%20no%20longer%20know%20how%20to%20be%20graceful%20in%20defeat.%20Cricket%20outshines%20all%20other%20sporting%20contests%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20command%20our%20attention%20and%20adulation.%20We%20are%20thus%20not%20very%20good%20particularly%20at%20taking%20a%20cricket%20defeat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20we%20were%20silently%20hoping%20for%20a%20genuine%20%E2%80%98national%20triumph%E2%80%99%20at%20Ahmedabad%2C%20a%20contest%20won%20(or%20lost)%20according%20to%20established%20rules%2C%20vigilantly%20and%20vigorously%20enforced%20by%20an%20external%20body%20and%20its%20neutral%20referees.%20Most%20of%20us%20feel%20in%20our%20bones%20that%20much%20of%20what%20we%20claim%20as%20%E2%80%98success%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98achievements%E2%80%99%20are%20carved%20out%20under%20dubious%20rules%20enforced%20by%20dubious%20and%20enfeebled%20umpires.%20Apart%20from%20a%20lustily%20cheering%20home%20crowd%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20boys%20had%20no%20undue%20advantage.%20Fair%20contests%2C%20fairly%20won%2C%20have%20a%20satisfying%20flavour%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20society%20feels%20the%20need%20for%20stars%20and%20winners%2C%20to%20bask%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20laurels%20of%20its%20sportsmen%20and%20sportswomen.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20we%20have%20managed%20to%20crowd%20heroes%20and%20achievers%20out%20of%20a%20national%20imagination%20that%20has%20not%20allowed%20to%20look%20beyond%20the%20%E2%80%98inspirational%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98visionary%E2%80%99%20leadership%20of%20one%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-australia-narendra-modi-stadium%5C%22%3EWatching%20Cricket%20%E2%80%93%20Now%20a%20Vehicle%20for%20the%20Political%20Elite%20%E2%80%93%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20institutionalised%20personality%20cult%20does%20not%20countenance%20any%20other%20iconic%20%E2%80%98achiever.%E2%80%99%20If%20we%20look%20unsentimentally%20at%20the%20leadership%20landscape%20in%20India%2C%20other%20than%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20there%20are%20no%20recognisable%20leader%20in%20any%20area%20of%20national%20activity.%20In%20a%20country%20that%20has%20supposedly%20elevated%20the%20soldiers%20and%20their%20generals%20to%20a%20new%20and%20higher%20status%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20officer%20commanding%20a%20national%20presence%3B%20the%20last%20soldier%20who%20sought%20limelight%20for%20himself%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fgeneral-bipin-rawat-cds-obituary%5C%22%3EGeneral%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20met%20an%20untimely%20death%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20business%20tycoon%20who%20seeks%20a%20national%20voice%20for%20himself%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20both%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20and%20Gautam%20Adani%20have%20wisely%20opted%20to%20keep%20a%20low%20profile%20and%20rarely%20allow%20the%20cameras%20in%20their%20vicinity.%20No%20film%20star%2C%20no%20religious%20leader%2C%20not%20even%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20chief%2C%20is%20allowed%20to%20eclipse%20the%20one%20and%20only%20one%20national%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20085636%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-8.56.27%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20085636%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-8.56.27%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20085636%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-8.56.27%25E2%2580%25AFAM-300x173.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F20085636%2FScreenshot-2023-11-20-at-8.56.27%25E2%2580%25AFAM-1024x591.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685464%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndia%20supporters%20at%20the%20world%20cup%20final%20with%20Australia%20on%20November%2019.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40cricketworldcup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20offers%20us%20a%20few%20sobering%20lessons%20in%20leadership.%20The%20four%20captains%20who%20led%20their%20teams%20into%20the%20semi-finals%20had%20one%20trait%20in%20common%3A%20a%20no-bragging%2C%20no-bombastic%20persona.%20Neither%20Kate%20Williamson%20(New%20Zealand)%20nor%20Temba%20Bavuma%20(South%20Africa)%20nor%20Patrick%20Cummins%20(Australia)%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(India)%20once%20gave%20the%20impre