0soaring%20inflation%20and%20rising%20poverty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EArgentina's%20Economy%20Minister%20Sergio%20Massa%20conceded%20defeat%20to%20populist%20Javier%20Milei%20in%20Sunday's%20fiercely%20polarized%20presidential%20runoff%20even%20before%20the%20country's%20electoral%20authority%20released%20official%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassa%20congratulated%20his%20opponent%2C%20a%20right-wing%20economist%20who%20has%20promised%20a%20dramatic%20shake-up%20for%20many%20of%20the%20nation's%20institutions%20and%20welcomed%20frequent%20comparisons%20of%20him%20to%20former%20U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20after%20Massa's%20concession%20speech%2C%20the%20Argentine%20electoral%20authority%20released%20partial%20results%3A%20With%2086.6%25%20of%20votes%20tallied%2C%20Milei%20had%2055.95%25%20and%20Massa%2044.04%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20Milei%20victory%2C%20the%20country%20will%20swing%20to%20the%20right%20amid%20discontent%20over%20soaring%20inflation%20and%20rising%20poverty%2C%20and%20empower%20a%20freshman%20lawmaker%20who%20describes%20himself%20as%20an%20anarcho-capitalist%20and%20got%20his%20start%20as%20a%20television%20talking%20head%20blasting%20what%20he%20called%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20caste.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20has%20soared%20above%20140%25%20and%20poverty%20has%20worsened%20while%20Massa%20has%20held%20his%20post.%20Milei%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fjavier-milei-argentina-elections-presidency-54671463bcf1a3ef22e7f7a2a602adcd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20self-described%20anarcho-capitalist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20proposed%20to%20slash%20the%20size%20of%20the%20state%20and%20rein%20in%20inflation%2C%20while%20the%20government%20minister%20he%20was%20running%20against%20warned%20people%20about%20the%20negative%20impacts%20of%20such%20policies.%20The%20election%20forced%20many%20to%20decide%20which%20of%20the%20two%20they%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20least%20bad%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilei's%20screeds%20resonated%20widely%20with%20Argentines%20angered%20by%20their%20struggle%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20particularly%20young%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20covers%20less%20and%20less%20each%20day.%20I'm%20a%20qualified%20individual%2C%20and%20my%20salary%20isn't%20enough%20for%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Esteban%20Medina%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20physical%20therapist%20from%20Ezeiza%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20Milei%20rally%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassa%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20figures%20in%20a%20deeply%20unpopular%20administration%2C%20was%20once%20seen%20as%20having%20little%20chance%20of%20victory.%20But%20he%20managed%20to%20mobilize%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fargentina-election-peronism-massa-milei-f5db5a92328f4316384ff6e0092c5272%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20networks%20of%20his%20Peronist%20party%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20clinched%20a%20decisive%20first-place%20finish%20in%20the%20first%20round%20of%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20campaign%20cautioned%20Argentines%20that%20his%20libertarian%20opponent's%20plan%20to%20eliminate%20key%20ministries%20and%20otherwise%20sharply%20curtail%20the%20state%20would%20threaten%20public%20services%2C%20including%20health%20and%20education%2C%20and%20welfare%20programs%20many%20rely%20on.%20Massa%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20his%20opponent's%20often%20aggressive%20rhetoric%20and%20openly%20questioned%20his%20mental%20acuity%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%20first%20round%2C%20Milei%20sometimes%20carried%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmilei-argentina-chainsaw-fed35a37c6137b951e4adada3d866436%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevving%20chainsaw%20at%20rallies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp