94%20by%20hiring%20people%20from%20the%20last%20company%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20going%20to%20say%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20which%20means%20that%20the%20biggest%20loser%20if%20Altman%20can't%20be%20convinced%20to%20return%20isn't%20Altman.%20And%20it%20isn't%20OpenAI%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20Microsoft%20and%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20is%20like%20Mahomes%20to%20the%20Chiefs.%20Nadella%20recognizes%20this%20and%20losing%20Sam%20is%20not%20an%20option.%20This%20OpenAI%20board%20is%20way%20over%20its%20head%20and%20the%20failed%20coup%20is%20now%20backfiring%2C%26quot%3B%20investor%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Webush%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20invested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-01-23%2Fmicrosoft-makes-multibillion-dollar-investment-in-openai%23xj4y7vzkg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20reported%20%2410%2B%20billion%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20owns%20a%20sizeable%20stake%20%E2%80%94%20some%20reports%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barrons.com%2Farticles%2Fmicrosoft-stock-openai-chatgpt-stake-value-ai-5de2525c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esay%20as%20much%20as%2049%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20for-profit%20unit%20run%20by%20the%20non-profit%20OpenAI.%20(Although%20Microsoft%20has%20never%20publicly%20confirmed%20the%20size%20of%20that%20stake.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20non-profit%20was%20run%20by%20a%20six-person%20governing%20board%20who%20owned%20no%20equity%20and%20included%20Altman%20and%20Brockman.%20So%20a%20simple%20majority%20vote%20was%20all%20it%20took%20to%20fire%20Altman%20and%20install%20CTO%20Mira%20Murati%20as%20interim%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-employees-shocked-at-altmans-ouster-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20Microsoft%20a%20few%20minutes%20advance%20warning%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20announcing%20Altman's%20ouster%2C%20sources%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20company%20has%2C%20publicly%20at%20least%2C%20stood%20by%20the%20board's%20decision.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20long-term%20agreement%20with%20OpenAI%20with%20full%20access%20to%20everything%20we%20need%20to%20deliver%20on%20our%20innovation%20agenda%20and%20an%20exciting%20product%20roadmap%3B%20and%20remain%20committed%20to%20our%20partnership%2C%20and%20to%20Mira%20and%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20Nadella%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20Friday%2C%20Microsoft's%20deal%20with%20OpenAI%20was%20a%20major%20coup%20for%20Nadella%2C%20giving%20Microsoft%20deep%20access%20to%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20center%20of%20AI%2C%20while%20preventing%20its%20competitors%20from%20doing%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20should%20Altman%20refuse%20to%20return%20and%20instead%20form%20a%20new%20AI%20startup%2C%20he%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-kicked-off-a-flood-of-emoji-posts-from-openai-executives-what-do-they-mean-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecertainly%20easily%20fill%20it%20with%20the%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20know%20the%20secrets%20of%20OpenAI%20technology.%20And%20he's%20also%20likely%20to%20seek%20another%20cloud%20investor%2Fpartner.%20Generative%20AI%20needs%20massive%2C%20specialized%20compute%20power%20to%20perform%2C%20especially%20to%20perform%20for%20millions%20of%20customers.%20Google%20or%20Amazon%20would%20almost%20certainly%20try%20to%20make%20Altman%20a%20deal%20he%20couldn't%20refuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20much%20safer%20for%20Nadella%20to%20pressure%20OpenAI%20into%20getting%20Altman%20to%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20worry%20is%20the%20Altman%20sweepstakes%20end%20up%20in%20the%20Google%20or%20Amazon%20backyard%20which%20would%20be%20a%20nightmare%20for%20Microsoft%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20wrote%20in%20a%20research%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20money%20invested%2C%20and%20the%20gains%20of%20that%20investment%2C%20that%20would%20be%20lost%20for%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20has%20been%20baking%20OpenAI%20technology%20into%20pretty%20much%20all%20of%20its%20major%20products%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-thursday-night-football-ad-100-million-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeating%20its%20rivals%20to%20market.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%20the%20company%20made%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-microsoft-employees-shocked-at-altmans-ouster-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E100%20announcements%20of%20integrations%20with%3C%2Fa%3E%20OpenAI%20tech%20across%20Microsoft's%20AI%20tools%2C%20AI%20models%2C%20tools%20in%20its%20cloud%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20put%20Copilot%20%E2%80%94%20its%20chat%20assistant%20based%20on%20GPT%20%E2%80%94%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Microsoft%20has%20also%20been%20making%20cuts%2C%20or%20outright%20winding%20down%2C%20various%20other%20internal%20homegrown%20AI%20projects%20to%20lean%20into%20OpenAI%20tech%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20shut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-shutters-project-airsim-ai-strategy-openai-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edown%20various%20%26quot%3Bindustrial%20metaverse%26quot%3B%20projects%20and%20laid%20off%20%3C%2Fa%3Estaff%2C%20as%20BI%20previously%20reported.%20That%20homegrown%20%26quot%3Bindustrial%20metaverse%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20a%20key%20AI%20strategy%20before%20ChatGPT%20took%20off%20like%20it%20did%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20means%20that%20if%20OpenAI%20up%20and%20implodes%2C%20Microsoft%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20fast%20backup%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20various%20reports%20%E2%80%94%20and%20just%20plain%20common%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20say%20that%20Altman%20won't%20come%20back%20unless%20the%20management%20structure%20of%20OpenAI%20is%20altered%2C%20and%20the%20four%20board%20members%20who%20fired%20him%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShould%20that%20happen%2C%20Microsoft%20could%20actually%20wind%20up%20in%20a%20better%20position%20to%20influence%20this%20all-important%20company%20that%20seems%20to%20need%20badly%20need%20the%20guidance%2C%20probably%20with%20a%20board%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20growing%20consensus%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20Wall%20Street%20is%20that%20the%20days%20for%20this%20four-person%20board%20are%20numbered%20and%20Altman%20will%20be%20back%20at%20OpenAI%20and%20ultimately%20Microsoft%20in%20an%20even%20stronger%20position%20to%20control%20OpenAI's%20strategic%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltman-openai-nightmare-microsoft-investor-says-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700429076000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655a72f39c7d23cb3b9d26ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltman-openai-nightmare-microsoft-investor-says-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20OpenAI%20up%20and%20implodes%2C%20Microsoft%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20fast%20AI%20tech%20backup%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbort%40insider.com%20(Julie%20Bort)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A101%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltman-openai-nightmare-microsoft-investor-says-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Ballad%20of%20Songbirds%20and%20Snakes%E2%80%99%20Nears%20%24100%20Million%20Globally.%20Is%20It%20Enough%20to%20Justify%20More%20%E2%80%98Hunger%20Games%E2%80%99%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publis