0src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19213644%2FF_S_d60bcAAGX_8.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20may%20not%20be%20a%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20elections%20to%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20on%20November%2030%2C%20but%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20mar%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20at%20a%20resurgence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20in%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%202018%20was%20only%206.98%25%2C%20but%20it%20shot%20up%20to%2019.65%25%20in%20the%20parliament%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20the%20following%20year%20on%20the%20back%20of%20nationwide%20outcry%20against%20the%20terror%20attack%20in%20Pulwama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETelangana%20went%20to%20polls%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20first%20of%20seven%20phases%20that%20began%20on%20April%2011%2C%202019%2C%20two%20months%20after%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20then%20won%20four%20seats%20for%20its%2019.65%25%20vote%20share%20and%20followed%20this%20up%20with%20victory%20in%2048%20out%20of%20150%20municipal%20divisions%20in%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC)%20elections%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EGoing%20by%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20past%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20has%20stakes%20in%2023%20assembly%20segments.%20They%20include%20Goshamahal%2C%20where%20it%20experienced%20its%20lone%20victory%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%3B%2020%20segments%20of%20four%20constituencies%20where%20it%20was%20in%20first%20place%20in%20the%202019%20parliament%20elections%3B%20and%20Huzurabad%20and%20Dubbaka%20constituencies%2C%20which%20it%20subsequently%20wrested%20in%20by-elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20436px)%2085vw%2C%20436px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22436%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20remained%20a%20force%20in%20the%20state%20under%20the%20stewardship%20of%20Karimnagar%20MP%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20until%20he%20was%20abruptly%20replaced%20by%20Union%20tourism%20minister%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20four%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20going%20has%20not%20been%20smooth%20for%20Reddy%2C%20as%20the%20party%20has%20found%20itself%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20because%20of%20its%20loss%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20defeat%20had%20a%20cascading%20effect%20in%20Telangana%2C%20where%20the%20party%20is%20fighting%20the%20polls%20without%20much%20hope%2C%20though%20it%20has%20fielded%20candidates%20in%20all%20119%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EBut%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20danger%20of%20the%20party%20playing%20spoilsport%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20Telangana%20Congress%20committee%20working%20president%20B.%20Mahesh%20Kumar%20Goud%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20this%20possibility%2C%20but%20a%20former%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti%20MP%20and%20vice-chairman%20of%20the%20State%20Planning%20Board%2C%20B.%20Vinod%20Kumar%2C%20felt%20that%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20for%20that%20Congress%20now%20that%20it%20is%20in%20a%20straight%20contest%20with%20the%20BRS%2C%20because%20the%20BJP%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20picture.%20The%20BRS%20would%20have%20gained%20heavily%20in%20a%20triangular%20contest%20owing%20to%20a%20split%20in%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EFormer%20Union%20home%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%2C%20who%20was%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Thursday%2C%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20down%20but%20not%20out%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20whereas%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20out%E2%80%9D%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CHad%20BJP%20retained%20power%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20all%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20Congress%20in%20Telangana%20would%20have%20joined%20the%20party%20and%20made%20it%20a%20major%20force.%20The%20Congress%20would%20have%20been%20decimated%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Vinod%20Kumar.%20He%20also%20took%20names%20of%20some%20leaders%20who%20had%20lined%20up%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Five%20States%20Go%20to%20the%20Polls%2C%20the%20Power%20of%20the%20Poor%20Will%20Decide%20the%20Results%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-rajasthan-madhya-pradesh-mizoram-telangana-election%5C%22%3EAs%20Five%20States%20Go%20to%20the%20Polls%2C%20the%20Power%20of%20the%20Poor%20Will%20Decide%20the%20Results%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20is%20not%20perceived%20as%20a%20force%2C%20Vinod%20Kumar%20said%20the%20contest%20has%20boiled%20down%20to%20the%20BRS%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20N.V.%20Subhash%20denied%20that%20the%20party%20is%20a%20non-serious%20contestant%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20party%20had%20identified%20about%2045%20seats%20where%20it%20is%20strong%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20its%20vote%20share%20is%20expected%20to%20be%2030-32%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESubhash%20asked%20why%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20visit%20the%20state%20so%20many%20times%20if%20the%20BJP%20was%20not%20a%20serious%20contender.%20The%20party%20definitely%20wants%20to%20capture%20power%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EModi%20has%20visited%20Telangana%20four%20times%20since%20the%20release%20of%20the%20election%20schedule%20and%20is%20due%20to%20visit%20thrice%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESubhash%20denied%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20a%20spoiler%20to%20the%20chances%20of%20either%20the%20BRS%20or%20Congress.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20will%20mar%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chances%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAn%20argument%20that%20gained%20ground%20was%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20was%20to%20strengthen%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20BRS%20as%20the%20anti-incumbency%20vote%20will%20split.%20%E2%80%9CWherever%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20the%20first%20or%20second%20position%2C%20it%20is%20advantage%20BRS%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20former%20member%20of%20legislative%20council%20K.%20Nageshwar.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20elections%20were%20fought%20at%20the%20constituency%20level%20and%20not%20state%20level.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20party%20was%20constituency%20specific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Jana%20Samiti%20president%20M.%20Kodandaram%20agreed%20with%20this%20view%2C%20with%20a%20rider%20that%20the%20BRS%20will%20be%20pushed%20to%20third%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20strong.%20The%20Congress%20will%20be%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThere%20will%20be%20only%20two%20leading%20competitors%20in%20all%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20where%20BJP%20is%20weak%2C%20or%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThere%20were%20expectations%20three%20years%20ago%20that%20the%20BRS%20will%20fight%20the%20current%20elections%20against%20the%20BJP%20as%20it%20was%20on%20a%20high%20nite%20and%20aggressively%20steered%20by%20Sanjay%20Kumar.%20The%20Congress%20was%20pushed%20to%20the%20third%20place%20with%20a%20deplorable%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20by-elections%20and%20GHMC%20polls.%20Even%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20mainly%20targeted%20the%20BJP%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20vehemently.%20He%20dismissed%20the%20Congress%20as%20of%20no%20consequence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ERao%20changed%20his%20tune%20to%20train%20guns%20on%20the%20Congress%20in%20his%20public%20speeches%20after%20the%20elections%20in%20Karnataka.%20He%20has%20made%20the%20Congress%20the%20butt%20of%20his%20criticism%20in%20all%20his%20election%20rallies%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20polls%20on%20the%20plank%20of%20making%20a%20leader%20from%20the%20backward%20classes%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20conceding%20to%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes.%20The%20party%20organised%20separate%20public%20meetings%20with%20Modi%20on%20both%20issues.%20It%20appeared%20meaningless%20to%20promise%20a%20backward%20classes%20chief%20minister%20after%20removing%20an%20OBC%20leader%2C%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20from%20the%20post%20of%20state%20president%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Fear%20of%20Defeat%20or%20Clever%20Political%20Move%3F%20Why%20KCR%20is%20Contesting%20from%20Two%20Seats.%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-why-kcr-contesting-two-seats%5C%22%3EFear%20of%20Defeat%20or%20Clever%20Political%20Move%3F%20Why%20KCR%20is%20Contesting%20from%20Two%20Seats.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20party%20was%20obviously%20unable%20to%20pick%20up%20despite%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20regular%20visits%20recently.%20The%20party%20cadre%20was%20also%20disillusioned%20with%20the%20Union%20government%20going%20easy%20on%20BRS%20leaders%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam%20case.%20This%20raised%20suspicion%20in%20their%20mind%20of%20a%20secret%20understanding%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP.%20Religious%20polarisation%2C%20which%20was%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20party%2C%20also%20did%20not%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20BJP%20Telangana%20manifesto%20committee%20chairman%20and%20former%20MP%20G.%20Vivek%20Venkatswamy%20and%20another%20former%20MP%20Vijayashanti%20quit%20the%20BJP%20to%20join%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700410577000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19213644%2FF_S_d60bcAAGX_8.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-bjp-isnt-a-frontrunner-but-could-it-be-a-spoilsport%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Observers%20think%20there%20will%20be%20only%20two%20leading%20competitors%20in%20all%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20BRS%20and%20Congress%20where%20BJP%20is%20weak%2C%20or%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20strong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-bjp-isnt-a-frontrunner-but-could-it-be-a-spoilsport%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20Office%3A%20%E2%80%98Hunger%20Games%E2%80%99%20Prequel%20Lands%20on%20Top%20With%20%2444%20Million%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Marvels%E2%80%99%20Collapses%20With%20Historic%2079%25%20Drop%22%