20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19162810%2FF_H0xndXcAAdd-S.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatan%20(Chhattisgarh)%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ESeema%20Sahu%2C%20a%20small%20general%20store%20owner%20in%20Motipur%20village%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Durg%20district%2C%20opened%20her%20shop%20earlier%20than%20usual%20on%20Friday.%20Her%20store%2C%20located%20on%20the%20road%20to%20Patan%2C%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf%2C%20is%20located%20right%20in%20front%20of%20the%20government%20school%20designated%20as%20the%20polling%20booth%20in%20their%20village.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20morning%2C%20Congress%20workers%20have%20been%20coming%20and%20buying%20various%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sahu%20says%2C%20even%20as%20less%20than%20150%20metres%20away%2C%20steaming%20hot%20plates%20of%20fried%20fritters%20arrive%20on%20the%20table%20at%20a%20makeshift%20pandal%20where%20Congress%20agents%20are%20sitting.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20Pramil%20Sahu%2C%20is%20Seema%E2%80%99s%20brother-in-law.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sure%20of%20Baghel%20Kaka%E2%80%99s%20win.%20We%20are%20just%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20wins%20with%20a%20huge%20margin.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20311px)%2085vw%2C%20311px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22311%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22257%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20Congress%20flags%20of%20all%20sizes%20dominate%20Kuruddih%2C%20Motipur%20and%20nearby%20Jheent%2C%20Tulsi%20village%2C%20in%20the%20same%20tehsil%2C%20flies%20flags%20of%20the%20Janta%20Congress%20Chhattisgarh%20(J)%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20too.%20Near%20the%20polling%20booth%20in%20Tulsi%2C%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20agents%20are%20sitting%20across%20the%20main%20road.%20While%20the%20Congress%20workers%20have%20a%20steady%20input%20of%20fried%20fritters%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20offering%20fruits%20to%20the%20voters%20coming%20to%20their%20pandal%20to%20check%20for%20their%20names.%20%E2%80%9CVijay%20Baghel%20is%20a%20worthy%20candidate%20who%20lived%20and%20worked%20among%20his%20people%20even%20after%20becoming%20an%20MP.%20We%20have%20full%20faith%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhatija%3C%2Fem%3E%20(nephew)%20will%20win%20against%20Kaka%20(Kaka%20is%20an%20endearing%20term%20used%20for%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anoop%20Sahu%2C%20a%20BJP%20worker%20from%20Tulsi%20village%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20voting%20for%2070%20constituencies%20complete%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20fates%20of%20over%20a%20thousand%20candidates%20have%20been%20sealed%20in%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20While%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20election%20held%20on%20November%207%20saw%20a%20weak%20voter%20turnout%2C%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20election%20saw%20long%20queues%20in%20most%20polling%20booths.%20The%20voter%20turnout%20percentage%2C%20however%2C%20recorded%20a%20slight%20decrease%20from%202018%2C%20with%2075.08%25%20voter%20turnout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20minister%20Baghel%20stood%20in%20a%20line%20at%20his%20home%20village%20of%20Kuruddih%2C%20in%20Patan%20constituency%2C%20to%20cast%20a%20vote%20around%20noon.%20While%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20is%20losing%2C%20we%20are%20coming%20back.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20fought%20the%20election%20on%20my%20face%3B%20still%20the%20party%20high%20command%20will%20decide%20who%20becomes%20the%20CM%20after%20we%20win.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20highest%20voter%20turnout%20was%20in%20Sanjari%20Balod%20constituency%20in%20Balod%20district%20with%2079.63%25%20and%20the%20lowest%20was%20recorded%20in%20Raipur%20(south)%20with%2052.11%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22At%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan's%20'Yogi'%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahant-baba-balaknath-rajasthan-election-yogi-adityanath%5C%22%3EAt%20Tijara%2C%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Yogi%E2%80%99%20Talks%20of%20Rising%20Above%20Caste%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20villages%20in%20Bilaspur%20region%E2%80%99s%20Masturi%20constituency%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20election%20and%20even%20demonstrated%20in%20front%20of%20the%20district%20officials%20who%20had%20come%20to%20try%20and%20dissuade%20them%20from%20their%20boycott.%20According%20to%20the%20residents%2C%20the%20boycott%20was%20called%20after%20none%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20took%20seriously%20their%20complaints%20of%20not%20having%20a%20motorable%20road%20connecting%20them%20to%20the%20nearby%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20fought%20the%20election%20on%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20his%20tenure%20of%20five%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20made%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20Baghel.%20Both%20the%20parties%20tried%20to%20one-up%20the%20other%20in%20their%20manifestos%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20declaring%20a%20scheme%20like%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Mahtari%20Vandan%20just%20days%20before%20the%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20also%20pitched%20for%20Hindu%20votes%20by%20targeting%20conversions%20and%20inter-religious%20marriages%20across%20various%20districts%20in%20the%20plains.%20In%20Saja%20constituency%2C%20Bemetara%2C%20the%20BJP%20gave%20its%20ticket%20to%20Ishwar%20Sahu%2C%20father%20of%20Bhuneshwar%20Sahu%20who%20had%20died%20allegedly%20in%20a%20Hindu-Muslim%20clash%20in%202021%2C%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20minister%20Ravindra%20Chaubey.%20The%20Congress%2C%20while%20not%20openly%20fighting%20for%20Hindu%20votes%2C%20had%20not%20shied%20away%20from%20adopting%20a%20soft%20Hindutva%20approach%20across%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20had%20fielded%20Mahant%20Ram%20Sundar%20Das%20of%20the%20Doodhadhari%20Math%20against%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20minister%20Brijmohan%20Agarwal%20in%20Raipur%20(south)%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20many%20within%20the%20party%20believed%20was%20promised%20to%20mayor%20Dhebar.%20The%20fight%20over%20the%20seat%20turned%20dramatic%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%2C%20as%20Agarwal%20alleged%20the%20Congress%20had%20organised%20an%20attack%20on%20him%20while%20he%20was%20campaigning%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20might%20lose%20some%20votes%20from%20minority%20communities%20like%20the%20tribal%20or%20Christian%20voters%20to%20small%20parties%20like%20Hamar%20Raj%20and%20Sarv%20Adi%20Dal.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20for%20the%20Congress%20is%20also%20the%20Sahu%20community%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20OBC%20groups%2C%20who%20feel%20sidelined%20by%20the%20ruling%20government.%20The%20BJP%20has%20actively%20worked%20on%20gaining%20support%20from%20the%20Sahu%20community%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20Says%20Congress%20Failed%20To%20'Control%20Naxal%20Violence%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20Data%20Shows%20Otherwise%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-narendra-modi-congress-naxal-violence-union-government-data%5C%22%3EModi%20Says%20Congress%20Failed%20To%20%E2%80%98Control%20Naxal%20Violence%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20Government%20Data%20Shows%20Otherwise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20political%20analysts%2C%20the%20elections%20in%20both%20phases%20across%20the%20state%20are%20unlike%20any%20held%20before%2C%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20common%20wave.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202018%2C%20it%20was%20an%20anti-incumbency%20wave%20and%20before%20that%2C%20Raman%20Singh%20was%20a%20strong%20factor.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20contest%20is%20between%20individual%20contestants%2C%20and%20each%20seat%20has%20its%20own%20dynamics%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20veteran%20political%20leader%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%2060%20seats%2C%20the%20Congress%20appears%20sure%20it%20will%20win%2075%20seats.%20However%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98war%20rooms%E2%80%99%20of%20both%20parties%20are%20struggling%20to%20get%20ground%20intelligence%20on%20the%20booth%20level.%20The%20results%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700392533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F19162810%2FF_H0xndXcAAdd-S.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-with-no-common-wave-in-sight-congress-bjp-train-eyes-on-december-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20Congress%20fought%20the%20election%20on%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20face%20and%20his%20tenure%20of%20five%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20made%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20Baghel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-w