%80%99.%20The%20online%20trolls%20called%20her%20%E2%80%98skinny%E2%80%99%20and%20were%20brutal%20to%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nancy%20showed%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20tougher%20than%20them.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20negative%20comments%20affect%20her%2C%20and%20worked%20steadfastly%20towards%20her%20purpose%20which%20was%20to%20help%20her%20mom%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20started%20working%20in%20a%20factory%20after%20we%20moved%20to%20Delhi.%20My%20father%20refused%20to%20support%20us%20financially%20as%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20me%20to%20move%20outside%20for%20further%20studies.%20My%20mother%20was%20my%20rock%20and%20brought%20me%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329864%2Fiit-delhi-grads-siddhant-jain-vibhav-sinha-founded-vdocipher-data-encryption-video-piracy-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eagainst%20our%20family%E2%80%99s%20wishes.%20She%20would%20come%20home%20covered%20in%20coal%20dust%20everyday%2C%20doing%20physical%20labour%20there%2C%20just%20to%20fulfil%20my%20dreams%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Nancy%2C%20the%20problems%20in%20real%20life%2C%20be%20it%20financial%2C%20or%20watching%20her%20mother%20struggle%2C%20were%20far%20greater%20than%20a%20comment%20on%20social%20media.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time%20to%20be%20bothered%20by%20it%20as%20she%20was%20busy%20hustling%20to%20give%20her%20mother%20a%20better%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20powerhouse%20of%20talent%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwhKKuTJq72%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCwhKKuTJq72%2F%3Futm_source%3Di