of%20coffee%20plantations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grow%20orchids%20on%20coffee%20trunks%20as%20these%20plants%20do%20not%20grow%20on%20trees%20with%20thick%20foliage.%20It%20is%20easier%20to%20fix%20the%20plant%20roots%20of%20orchids%20on%20the%20soft%20trunk%20of%20coffee%20plants.%20Coffee%20plantations%20allow%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20diffused%20sunlight%20to%20stream%20in%20on%20them%20every%20day.%20Here%2C%20orchids%20are%20protected%20by%20direct%20harsh%20sunlight%20and%20heavy%20rain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20he%20has%20replanted%20around%20200%20saplings%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235243%2Fkerala-orchid-how-to-grow-cultivation-business-homemaker-earns-lakhs-urban-garden-ser106%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewild%20orchids%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20and%20has%20cultivated%20around%20120%20native%20varieties%20of%20wild%20orchids%20at%20his%20home%2C%20of%20these%2060%20are%20from%20Western%20Ghats.%20He%20has%20also%20planted%204%2C000%20plants%20of%20commercial%20orchids%20at%20home%20in%20three%20poly%20houses%20spread%20across%20750%20square%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESabu%20also%20claims%20to%20have%20discovered%20a%20hybrid%20orchid%20species%2C%20which%20he%20named%20%E2%80%98Benita%E2%80%99%20after%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-4-1700226488.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sabu%20has%20received%20many%20awards%20for%20his%20work.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-4-1700226488.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSabu-4-1700226488-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-medi