20a%20homestay%20business.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20different%20to%20attract%20more%20people.%20I%20started%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20thought%20of%20making%20Igloos%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ideal%20temperature%20for%20an%20Igloo%20to%20be%20made%20is%20-20%20degrees%20Celsius.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20temperatures%20at%20Manali%20are%20not%20ideal%20for%20an%20Igloo%20to%20survive%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20them%20in%20Sethan%20Village%20where%20the%20temperatures%20go%20as%20low%20as%20-12%20degrees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Vinod%20was%20excited%20about%20making%20them%2C%20the%20challenge%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20knowledge.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20really%20knew%20how%20to%20make%20them%20back%20then%3B%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20proceed.%20My%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20make%20a%20steel%20frame%20for%20the%20Igloo%2C%20but%20in%20my%20research%2C%20I%20found%20that%20the%20metal%20would%20melt%20the%20snow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202016%20when%20he%20met%20an%20Australian%20man%20who%20had%20settled%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20spent%20some%20time%20in%20Alaska%20and%20knew%20the%20way%20an%20Igloo%20is%20made.%20He%20gave%20us%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20the%20science%20behind%20the%20construction%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFurthermore%2C%20we%20used%20the%20internet%20extensively%20to%20understand%20the%20process.%20I%20also%20used%20YouTube%20to%20see%20how%20people%20live%20in%20them%20and%20how%20sustainable%20they%20are%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20climate%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-