%20brave%20deep%20forests%2C%20remote%20areas%20and%20harsh%20terrain%2C%20are%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20year%2C%20it%20was%20Bengaluru-native%20Vihaan%20Talya%20Vikas%E2%80%99s%20photography%20that%20grabbed%20eyeballs.%20The%2010-year-old%E2%80%99s%20winning%20shot%20is%20telling%20in%20and%20of%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ornamental%20tree%20trunk%20spider%20preventing%20its%20prey%20from%20escaping%2C%20with%20a%20carving%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20in%20the%20frame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20shot%20bagged%20the%20prize%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9810%20years%20and%20under%E2%80%98%20category.%20This%20came%20as%20a%20pleasant%20surprise%20to%20the%20Class%205%20student%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20Kumaran%20School.%20%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20it%20was%20anticipated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20recalling%20the%20unassuming%20day%20he%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclicked%20the%20picture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20visiting%20a%20tamarind%20grove%20at%20Nalluru%20along%20with%20my%20dad%20and%20his%20friends.%20We%20stopped%20by%20the%20Gopalaswamy%20Temple%20to%20admire%20the%20carvings%20of%20Lord%20Krishna.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20spotted%20the%20spider%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20first%20thought%20was%2C%20how%20well-positioned%20the%20arachnid%20was.%20It%20almost%20seemed%20entranced%20by%20Lord%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20flute.%20Insects%2C%20particularly%20spiders%2C%20had%20always%20held%20a%20fancy%20for%20Vihaan%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20they%20spin%20webs%2C%20and%20hunt%20their%20prey%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20so%20cool%3F%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20He%20recalls%20spending%20hours%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332890%2Findian-photographers-pictures-military-navy-wildlife-oceans-astronomy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapturing%20their%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20childhood%20summer%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20was%20only%20natural%20that%20the%20young%20boy%20sat%20down%2C%20and%20watched%20the%20spider%20weave%20a%20wheel-shaped%20web%2C%20entangling%20any%20prey%20that%20dared%20to%20come%20too%20close.%20And%20soon%20he%20got%20clicking.%20%E2%80%9CI%20must%20have%20clicked%20over%20200%20pictures%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20among%20them%20was%20the%20winning%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vihaan's%20winning%20shot%20in%20the%20'10%20years%20and%20under'%20category%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20of%20the%20Year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fcarpet-business_20231116_192020_0000_11zon-1700143087-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334317%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVihaan%E2%80%99s%20winning%20shot%20in