%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20bring%20the%20second%20income%20in%20my%20home%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20period%20was%20about%2030%20days%20long%2C%20says%20Namita.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Gaurav%20sir%20asked%20us%20what%20are%20the%20uses%20of%20bamboo%2C%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20answer%20his%20question.%20We%20would%20sometimes%20use%20it%20to%20make%20carriers%20but%20that%20was%20it.%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20how%20many%20useful%20things%20can%20be%20made%20from%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20training%20period%20was%20over%2C%20we%20started%20to%20get%20some%20work.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20used%20to%20get%20fewer%20orders%2C%20but%20we%20kept%20working%20hard.%20Soon%2C%20we%20received%20more%20orders.%20I%20had%20faith%20that%20if%20we%20kept%20on%20working%2C%20the%20demand%20would%20increase%20and%20we%20would%20make%20more%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20we%20have%20now%20established%20a%20company%20by%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Vikramgad%20Bamboo%20Udyog%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%E2%80%99%20and%20we%20will%20soon%20be%20taking%20orders%20online%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20Namita%20now%20makes%20an%20average%20of%20Rs%209%2C000%20every%20month.%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20very%20proud%20that%20I%20am%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20household%20income.%20I%20finish%20my%20household%20work%2C%20then%20help%20my%20husband%20with%20the%20field%20work%20before%20proceeding%20to%20work%20on%20the%20bamboo%20pieces%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20adding%20that%20the%20work%20gives%20them%20the%20flexibility%20to%20take%20it%20up%20whenever%20they%20have%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F1